<h1>Učitaj XML fajl</h1>



@*input tipa fajl za izbor fajla stilizujemo bootstrap klasama najblize sto mozemo dizajnu,
    alternativa je css kod.*@
@*Ovu stranicu smo postavili kao pocetnu na sledeci nacin:
    https://social.msdn.microsoft.com/Forums/en-US/54f183ae-cf3b-439c-84d0-603e2be5a100/how-to-set-startup-page-with-area-in-aspnet-mvc-4?forum=aspmvc*@

@*Koristicemo HTTP metod POST za slanje fajla serveru jer ga onda kasnije dohvatamo lako pomocu Request objekta

    https://stackoverflow.com/questions/6439926/getting-the-name-of-file-just-uploaded-in-html-file-input-type
        https://www.slimframework.com/docs/v4/cookbook/uploading-files.html

    Stilizovanje input type="file" preko label:
    https://stackoverflow.com/questions/5813344/how-to-customize-input-type-file
*@

<form action="/Raspored" method="post">

    <p id="p">&emsp; XML datoteka</p>

    <div id="label_space">
        <!--u label i input type="submit" se mogu umesto dugme klase staviti bootstrap klase btn btn-outline-dark
        Custom stilizovanje inputa:
        https://www.w3schools.com/howto/howto_css_outline_buttons.asp

        -->
        <label for="FileInput" class="dugme">Izaberi</label>

    </div>
    <input id="FileInput" type="file" value="Izaberi" name="fileName" title="Izaberi" class="" style="display: none" />


    <br />
    <br />

    <input type="submit" name="submit" value="Učitaj" class="dugme" />

</form>
